Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:16.24,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫沃尔特·哈特维尔·怀特\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}My name is Walter Hartwell White.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.45,0:02:19.31,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在新墨西哥州阿尔布开克\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I live at 308 Negra Arroyo lane{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.35,0:02:21.93,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内格拉阿罗约巷308号  邮编87104\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Albuquerque New Mexico 87104.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:23.61,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要告诉所有的执法者\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}To all law enforcement entitles{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:25.40,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一段认罪声明\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}this is not an admission of guilt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.06,0:02:28.20,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我跟家人之间的对话\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I am speaking to my family now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:36.96,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯凯勒\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Skyler{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:39.63,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我今生的至爱\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You are the love of my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:41.81,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能了解这点\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I hope you know that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.06,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小沃尔特\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Walter Junior{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:47.48,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我心中你是个男子汉了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You're my big man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:49.82,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在接下来的几天里\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}There are{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:51.90,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}There are going to be some{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.94,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会知道\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Things things{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:55.43,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于我的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}That you'll come to{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.77,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于我的一些事情\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Learn about me in the next few days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:59.82,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想你们清楚一点\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I just want you to know{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:03.60,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么事\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}That no no matter how it may look{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.45,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心里牵挂的只有你们\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I only had you in my heart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.59,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Good-bye.{\r}
