Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.54,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日快乐\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Happy birthday.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:21.18,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧瞧这个\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Look at that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.12,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是素培根\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}That is veggie bacon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.68,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甭管你信不信  零胆固醇的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Believe it or not. zero cholesterol.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:29.09,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃起来也是一个味儿\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You won't even taste the difference.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:31.92,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得自己大概几点能到家\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}What time do you think you'll be home?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:32.99,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老时间\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Same time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:35.34,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望他又缠你一整晚\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I don't want him dicking you around tonight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:36.87,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的工资只给到5点\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You get paid till 5{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:38.96,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你工作到5点  这就行了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You work till 5 no later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:45.39,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-生日快乐啊  -谢谢\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}- Hey, happy birthday.  - Well, thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.38,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又起晚了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You're late again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:50.38,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没热水了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}There was no hot water again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.21,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个简单应对的办法\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I have an easy fix for that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:53.81,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早点起床\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You wake up early{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.84,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就可以第一个洗澡了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}And then you get to be the first person in the shower.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:58.48,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有个办法\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I have an idea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:04.90,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥不买个新热水器呢\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}How about buy a new hot water heater?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.10,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这主意如何\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}How's that idea?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:09.42,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都提了成千上万次了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}For the millionth and billionth time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.51,0:06:13.96,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-止咳药喝过没  -喝了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}- Did you take your echinacea?  - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.15,0:06:15.84,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得好多了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I think it's getting better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:19.33,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么鬼玩意儿啊\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}What the hell is this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:23.47,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素培根  我觉得我们该注意下胆固醇了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}It's veggie bacon. We're watching our cholesterol, I guess.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.47,0:06:25.60,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别给我  我要真培根\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Not me. I want real bacon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.44,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这假冒的破烂\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Not this fake crap.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:28.44,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟糕\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Too bad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.59,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Eat it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:32.94,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这闻上去就像创口贴\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}This smells like band-aids.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.06,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我吃了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Eat it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:42.08,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为老人家感觉怎么样\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}So how's it feel to be old?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.69,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当个小破孩感觉怎么样\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}How does it feel to be a smart ass?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.02,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对得好\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.76,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧吃吧\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Eat your veggie bacon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:11.13,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-准备好了吗  -好了  我能行\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}- You're all set? - Yeah, I'm fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.34,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那好  回家见  -再见\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}- All right, see you at home. - Okay, see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.44,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化学\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Chemistry{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:22.58,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是研究什么的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}It is the study of what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:24.80,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Anyone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:27.68,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本恩\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Ben.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:29.11,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化学品\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Chemicals?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.60,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化学品\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Chemicals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.78,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:35.68,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化学\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Chemistry is{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.28,0:07:37.67,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从学术层面说\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Well technically{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:40.43,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化学是一门研究物质的学科\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Chemistry is the study of matter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.49,0:07:44.96,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我更倾向于它是一门研究变化的学科\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}But I prefer to see it as the study of change.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:47.32,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  我们这样来设想一下\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Now just just think about this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:48.70,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电子\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Electrons.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:50.40,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}They{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.40,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变自身的能级\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Change their energy levels.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.59,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分子呢\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Molecules.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.78,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分子改变自身的化学键\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Molecules change their bonds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:07:59.81,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些元素\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Elements.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.84,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行组合从而形成化合物\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}They combine and change into compounds.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:06.28,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所有生命的组成形式\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Well that's that's all of life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:08.57,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对  我是说  这是个恒定的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Right? I mean it's just it's the constant.{\r}
