Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.81,0:30:20.40,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14美元  不算邮费\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Fourteen dollars plus shipping.{\r}
