Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.67,0:31:11.73,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什么  他挺好\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}What do you mean? He's fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.74,0:31:15.38,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他看起来有点\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}He just seems,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.49,0:31:17.06,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也说不清  他比平时话少\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I don't know. Quieter than usual.{\r}
