Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.29,0:33:04.55,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能用这种玩意制毒的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You wouldn't cook in on of these.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.20,0:33:06.61,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确实是\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Yeah I do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.05,0:33:08.59,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你不可能的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}No, you don't.{\r}
