Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.28,0:33:15.38,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以用来加热\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You wouldn't apply heat to a volumetric flask.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.41,0:33:17.59,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧瓶才可以加热\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}That's what a boiling flask is for.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.11,0:33:20.35,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的化学课你一点都没学到吗\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Did you learn nothing from my chemistry class?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.37,0:33:22.30,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  你挂我科了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}No. You flunked me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.91,0:33:24.48,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-记得吗  -难怪呢\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}- Remember? - No wonder.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.48,0:33:25.39,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Prick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.88,0:33:29.38,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你吧  这可不是化学课\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Now let me tell you something else. This ain't chemistry{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.52,0:33:31.04,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是艺术\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}This is art.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.99,0:33:33.56,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制毒是艺术\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Cooking is art.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.60,0:33:36.92,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我制的毒很赞  少对我说教\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}And the shit I cook is the bomb so don't be telling me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.92,0:33:38.99,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你制的那是垃圾\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}The shit you cook is shit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.56,0:33:41.61,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见过你的装备  太荒谬了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I saw your setup. Ridiculous.{\r}
