Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.44,0:33:46.37,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要制出稳定的化学纯产品\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}We will produce a chemically pure{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.38,0:33:48.70,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像广告宣传的一般\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}And stable product that performs as advertised.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.76,0:33:51.12,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不掺假  不掺奶粉  也不掺胡椒粉\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}No adulterants. No baby formula. No chili powder.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.12,0:33:53.85,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不  胡椒粉是我的标识\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}No no chili p is my signature.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.85,0:33:54.93,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Not anymore.{\r}
