Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.50,0:34:02.04,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这他妈什么玩意儿  -实验室防护用具\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}- What the hell is this?  - Lab safety equipment.{\r}
