Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.27,0:34:10.65,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我现在告诉你\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}In case you didn't know that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.65,0:34:13.45,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你乐意  你穿得像个同性恋都行\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Well you can dress up like a faggot if you want.{\r}
