Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.05,0:34:23.57,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好  这些东西最多只能在这放一天\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Listen this stuff doesn't stay more than a day.{\r}
