Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.52,0:47:48.77,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们俩都给毙了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I say we cap them both.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.68,0:47:58.63,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那批货真的是你制的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You really cook up that batch?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.25,0:48:01.36,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.47,0:48:02.92,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个艺术家\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You an artist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.06,0:48:06.35,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太可惜了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}It's a damn shame.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.60,0:48:08.87,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等一下\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Wait! Wait a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.21,0:48:11.35,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Listen to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.10,0:48:13.76,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把秘方给你们\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I'll teach you my recipe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.75,0:48:16.96,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚怎么说来着  也想造出这样的货\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}What do you say? You want to cook like me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.07,0:48:21.88,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了我们俩\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}You let us both live{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.15,0:48:24.87,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就教你们\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}And I will teach you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.82,0:48:58.19,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不许抽烟\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Put the cigarette out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.34,0:49:02.41,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.80,0:49:42.41,yingzimu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs8\bord0\fn黑体\pos(270,175)\1c&H000000&}红  磷
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.80,0:49:42.41,renwujianjie,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fn黑体\fs10\pos(5,250)}红磷:\N位于元素周期表第15位 元素符号P 紫红或略带棕色的无定形粉末\N有光泽 密度2.34克/厘米3 加热升华 但在4300千帕压强下加热\N至590℃可熔融 汽化后再凝华则得白磷 难溶于水和CS2 乙醚 氨等\N略溶于无水乙醇 无毒无气味 燃烧时产生白烟 烟有毒
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.80,0:49:42.41,kuangjia,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx300\fscy90\pos(83,270)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.64,0:49:48.02,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点  伙计\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Move it homes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.28,0:49:49.95,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那么多时间跟你耗\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}We ain't got all day.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.67,0:49:53.60,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.25,0:54:06.57,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}What happened?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.66,0:54:12.45,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么他们了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}What'd you do to them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.98,0:54:16.36,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潮湿状态下的红磷\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Red Phosphorus in the presence of moisture{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.36,0:54:19.89,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇热会加速产生磷化氢\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}And accelerated by heat yields Phosphorus Hydride.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.74,0:54:23.11,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一种剧毒气体\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Phosphine gas.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.91,0:54:25.24,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸入这么小小一口\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}One good whiff and{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.55,0:54:51.75,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}We gotta{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.25,0:54:56.73,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得  清理下现场\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}We gotta clean this up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.12,0:55:46.56,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Where were you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.01,0:55:55.87,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Walter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.28,0:56:02.23,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你最近怎么了  但是\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I don't know what's been going on with you lately but{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.23,0:56:04.58,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  我很好\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Nothing. I'm fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.80,0:56:06.42,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是怎么回事\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Whatever it is{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.20,0:56:08.81,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I'll tell you this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.65,0:56:12.58,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢你有事瞒着我\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}I do not like it when you don't talk to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.20,0:56:16.94,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最不济也就是把我甩了罢了\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}The worst thing you can do is shut me out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.92,0:57:11.14,duibai,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃尔特  那还是你吗\N{\fnCalibri Italic\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur2}Walter is that you?{\r}


